@item @strong{@asis{}-@asis{}-@asis{}wd} @emph{mydir}
@anchor{@strong{@asis{}-@asis{}-@asis{}wd} @emph{mydir}}

Jobs will be run in the dir @emph{mydir}. The default is the current dir
for the local machine, and the login dir for remote computers.

Files transferred using @strong{@asis{}-@asis{}-@asis{}transferfile} and @strong{@asis{}-@asis{}-@asis{}return} will be
